    "549742": {
      "title": "A duality for the algebras of a Lukasiewicz n + 1-valued modal system",
      "abstract": "In this paper, we develop a duality for the varieties of a Łukasiewicz n + 1-valued modal system. This duality is an extension of Stone duality for modal algebras. Some logical consequences (such as completeness results, correspondence theory...) are then derived and we propose some ideas for future research."
